data.description: Like new and move in ready. 3 bedroom 2 bath home built in 2023 on 1.5 acres.  Vaulted ceilings in great room and open floor plan.  Spacious kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances and kitchen island. Large laundry room off of kitchen offering additional storage space.  LVT flooring throughout home. Master bedroom with walk in closet and double vanities in master bathroom. Great property with room for a  shop or garage addition. Land is level and offers many possibilities for additional structures. No restrictions and No HOA!
